/meet.google.com/amz-oebc-bhe\">https://meet.google.com/amz-oebc-bhe</a><br>Youtube Live Stream: ¬†<a href=\"https://youtu.be/h5sEa2g4kvo\">https://youtu.be/h5sEa2g4kvo</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>L·ªãch tr√¨nh</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>20:00 &#8211; 20:15 &#8211; Ch√†o m·ª´ng<br>20:15 &#8211; 21:15 &#8211; Chia s·∫ª c√°c ch·ªß ƒë·ªÅ<br>21:15 &#8211; 21:30 &#8211; Th·∫£o lu·∫≠n v√† k·∫øt th√∫c</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Ch·ªß ƒë·ªÅ</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>&#8211; Static Site l√† g√¨ v√† √°p d·ª•ng Static Site trong WordPress &#8211; Nguy·ªÖn VƒÉn ƒê∆∞·ª£c<br>&#8211; T∆∞∆°ng lai c·ªßa Gutenberg Editor &#8211; Thi·ªán Nguy·ªÖn<br><br><strong>Chia s·∫ª ch·ªß ƒë·ªÅ c·ªßa b·∫°n</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>C√°c b·∫°n mu·ªën ƒëƒÉng k√≠ tham gia chia s·∫ª v·ªÅ m·ªôt topic n√†o ƒë√≥, vui l√≤ng h√£y ƒë·ªÉ l·∫°i comment b√™n d∆∞·ªõi ho·∫∑c nh·∫Øn tin qua h·ªá th·ªëng tin nh·∫Øn c·ªßa Meetup.com v√† ch√∫ng m√¨nh s·∫Ω li√™n h·ªá v·ªõi b·∫°n.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>===== English Content =====</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The official WordPress Meetup #28 in Ho Chi Minh City (aka Saigon) will be an Online Event.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The meetup is totally free to attend and is sponsored by Officience and Weglot.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Q&amp;A:¬†<a href=\"https://app.sli.do/event/m00pz11k\">https://app.sli.do/event/m00pz11k</a><br>Google Meet:¬†<a href=\"https://meet.google.com/amz-oebc-bhe\">https://meet.google.com/amz-oebc-bhe</a><br>Youtube Live Stream: ¬†<a href=\"https://youtu.be/h5sEa2g4kvo\">https://youtu.be/h5sEa2g4kvo</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Agenda</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>20:00 &#8211; 20:15 &#8211; Welcome<br>20:15 &#8211; 21:15 &#8211; Talks<br>21:15 &#8211; 21:30 &#8211; Open discussion and closing</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Talks</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>&#8211; What is static site? How to apply it to WordPress &#8211; Nguy·ªÖn VƒÉn ƒê∆∞·ª£c<br>&#8211; The future of Gutenberg Editor &#8211; Thi·ªán Nguy·ªÖn<br><br><strong>Be a speaker!</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you would like to sign up for a talk, please comment down below or mes